The heart calms down in the flickering of flames.... \! The
party's health has been fully restored!

\SE[0]That's good. The water here seems to be clean.
\SE[0]If we store it, it should be fine for a while.

\SE[0]Thank you, Melissa. \SE[0]Since the Yurisene is also
close, let's take a little break. \SE[20]...You are
hardworking and I really appreciate it, but...

\SE[21]Oh my, however... Crossing mountains, crossing
valleys... \SE[0]It was such a long journey to get here.
\SE[1]I never thought it would turn into such a great
adventure.

\SE[24]Ugh... I'm sorry... If my directions were perfect, we
would have already arrived at Yurisene a long time ago...

\SE[16]Ahaha...! I had fun though. \SE[1]It felt like a
self- sufficient survival...!

\SE[16]And I also learned a lot from Nikita's way of making
money. \SE[15]I wonder just how many special nights they
have experienced.

\SE[56]Because it's a maiden's secret, \.we mustn't let it
leak to the outside, okay?

\SE[12]Ugh... I'm so tired. Ah, I need to rest. \SE[4]Ah, my
body... It hurts so much... Ouch.

\SE[12]Honestly, I was impressed by that technique.
\SE[14]It could become an accurate guide for my future life.
\SE[38]But you know... \SE[51]Hey, do I have to say this
too?

\SE[44]The swaying 'breasts' along the way were truly a
feast for the eyes. \SE[43] Even when I was a little tired,
just catching a glimpse of them would rejuvenate me. \SE[12]
So please, continue in this manner from now on.
\SE[12]...because.

\SE[15]Hey Ronoa, wanna sleep together today? I'll give you
lots of hugs and pamper you like a baby.

\SE[46]That thing I showed you the other day...
\!\SE[15]Should I do it for Ronoa-chan too?

\SE[14]A succubus who seduces people with her bewitching big
breasts...!! \SE[13]No matter how intense... the temptation
may be...!! \SE[44]I... I will never lose...!!
\SE[1]...Because.

\SE[0]Yes, I understand. \SE[0]If you ever want to become a
baby, feel free to reach out to me. I'll pamper you as much
as you want.
\SE[16]Ahaha. This is Ronoa's defeat, isn't it?

\SE[3] (Even though they're acting tough... Both of them
must be at their physical limits...)

\SE[13] (I can't spend any more time. I need to quickly take
the two of them to a safe place... \SE[42] ...It's okay.
Just a little more... Just a little more, that's all.)

\SE[0]Did you drink too much water? \!\SE[0]If so, why don't
you just go pee in that river over there? \!\SE[2]After all,
there's no one else here but us.

\SE[4]Ah... It's dangerous to be alone on the night road,
so...
